 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I spent seven years full-time in a 2017 Dodge ProMaster 2500, and one underrated upgrade was replacing the factory head unit with a more capable navigation and media system. Good route planning, better audio integration, and smoother device connectivity improve daily drive quality and reduce friction on long travel days. This review covers the Kenwood DNX574S from that real-use perspective.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Bluetti Charger 1 Alternator Charger Review for Camper Vans</title><link>https://gwinn092.github.io/van.affiliation/gear/bluetti-charger-1-alternator-charger-review/</link><pubDate>Fri, 20 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://gwinn092.github.io/van.affiliation/gear/bluetti-charger-1-alternator-charger-review/</guid><description>&lt;h1 class="relative group"&gt;Bluetti Charger 1 Alternator Charger Review for Camper Vans
