 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I spent seven years living full-time in a 2017 Dodge ProMaster 2500, and one lesson never changed: ventilation is foundational. It is easy to overspend on gadgets and underspend on airflow. The MaxxAir 4500K is often considered the value option in this category, so I tested it as a real daily-use solution and compared it with higher-end alternatives.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>MaxxAir MaxxFan Deluxe 7500K Review: Best Fan for Van Life?</title><link>https://gwinn092.github.io/van.affiliation/gear/maxxair-maxxfan-deluxe-7500k-review/</link><pubDate>Fri, 20 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://gwinn092.github.io/van.affiliation/gear/maxxair-maxxfan-deluxe-7500k-review/</guid><description>&lt;h1 class="relative group"&gt;MaxxAir MaxxFan Deluxe 7500K Review: Best Fan for Van Life?
